p: Crude endophyte extracts from Raoultella ornithinolytica displayed 43% cell reduction at 100 μg/mL against A549 lung carcinoma cells. Protein complex from R. ornithinolytica has shown anticancer activity against HeLa cell line, human endometrioid ovarian cancer line (TOV 112D ATCC CRL-11731), and the human breast adenocarcinoma line (T47D ECACC 85102201) resulting in cytopathic effect and reduction in the cell number [ 91, 92].
